video_title: Will you put it into practice? #adviceoftheday #motivation #mindset #growth #grattitude
transcript:
the older I get the more I realize how
important it is to be grateful for
everything that I already have and to
stop crying and bitching and moaning
about all the things that I don't have
like if you look around you you'll
really realize how much you have to be
grateful for realize how much you've
actually been blessed in your life some
people would kill to have your life and
you're crying about it because when you
focus on gratitude and being grateful
every single day God or the universe or
whatever it is that's out there is going
to bless you with more things to be
grateful for
